      "title": "NIMH\u2019s Mental Health Helpline via WhatsApp",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Airtel Lanka, in collaboration with the National Institute of Mental Health (NIMH), announced a major expansion of the 1926 mental health helpline through the WhatsApp service. Anyone in need of mental health assistance can reach NIMH's Mental Health Helpline via WhatsApp on 075 555 1926. Pix by Pradeep Dilrukshana"
      ],
